@PeteAndIsh @Tesla Yes. Range is definitely important. I rue not buying the 100D Model C. But having said that, the number of Charging options are increasing around Australia. I travel every week to Sydney from Wollongong and have not had any range anxiety issue yet. Perhaps on a longer journey!?!

@AutoElectrified @TeslaTripping I initially used to have % and argued that I know that metric from my phone and iPad usage days. But now I’m more comfortable with kms left. So when I plan a trip I know that it’s doable. No range anxiety. And yes @Tesla let’s us choose.
